  "title": "Drawer",
  "description": "Adds drawers to the game",
  "body": "# Currently, 1.21 only has Neoforge support\n\n<h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hzPG2In.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"37\" height=\"37\">&nbsp; Features</h1>\n<p>Drawer mod&nbsp;adds Drawers to the game with wooden variants &amp; also stripped wooden variants &amp; also stripped wooden.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The mod also adds screws &amp; a painting to the game</p>\n<p>There are also stripped versions of the drawer</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/526/70/2022-11-24-23.png\" alt=\"All blocks &amp; items\" width=\"661\" height=\"372\"></p>\n<p>(All blocks &amp; items)</p>\n<p>Drawer works with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://files.minecraftforge.net/net/minecraftforge/forge/\">Forge</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://fabricmc.net/\">Fabric</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://quiltmc.org/en/\">Quilt</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neoforged.net/\">Neoforge</a>.</p>\n<p>Quilt version reqiures&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/qsl\">Quilted Fabric API</a></p>\n<h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EeCzuL1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"37\" height=\"37\">&nbsp;Crafting/Smelting Recipe</h1>\n<p>The crafting recipe are 7 screws any plank &amp; any log/stem</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/808/978/ezgif.gif\" alt=\"the crafting recipe\" width=\"388\" height=\"203\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<br><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/808/980/ezgif.gif\" alt=\"the crafting recipe for stripped drawers\" width=\"388\" height=\"203\"></p>\n<p>The smelting recipe 1 iron nugget</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/818/743/2023-03-16-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"388\" height=\"203\"></p>\n<h1>📃 Credits</h1>\n<p>Credit to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://freesound.org/people/Aesterial-Arts/\">Aesterial-Arts</a>&nbsp;for the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://freesound.org/people/Aesterial-Arts/sounds/633915/\">open</a>&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://freesound.org/people/Aesterial-Arts/sounds/633838/\">close</a>&nbsp;sounds</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://freesound.org/people/Aesterial-Arts/sounds/633915/\">Open</a>&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://freesound.org/people/Aesterial-Arts/sounds/633838/\">close</a>&nbsp;sounds are licensed as&nbsp;<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/\">CC BY 4.0</a></p>\n<p>This mod was created using&nbsp;<a href=\"https://mcreator.net/\">MCreator</a></p>\n<h1>🔗 Links</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/drawer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vdhPo3Q.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"219\" height=\"84\"></a>&nbsp; <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/drawer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gjZ8Yew.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"219\" height=\"84\"></a> &nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/mod/drawer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qTdhZxS.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"219\" height=\"84\"></a> &nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://mcreator.net/modification/92529/drawer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/O65WM2Y.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"219\" height=\"84\"></a> &nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/EntzoMC/Drawer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Hpid0S0.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"219\" height=\"84\"></a> &nbsp;<a href=\"https://entzomc.com/mods\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ByW9nP5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"218\" height=\"84\"></a></p>\n<p>Drawer mod is Open Source! 🎉 to visit GitHub repo,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/EntzoMC/drawer\">click here</a></p>\n<p>Check out the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://entzomc.com/mods\">Official website</a></p>\n<p>Join my&nbsp;<a title=\"Discord Server\" href=\"https://discord.com/invite/9dqH4Qgane\">Discord Server</a></p>",
